## EPIC-09: Admin Dashboard & Operations

**Priority:** P1 (Should Have)  
**Description:** Administrative tools for system monitoring, issue triage, user support, and extraction diagnostics.  
**Business Value:** Enables operations team to maintain system health and resolve user issues.  
**Dependencies:** All other epics, Monitoring Infrastructure

